      "body": "Anecdotally, this appears to be fixed with current master.\nI started syncing on a 32-bit 4-core ARM box yesterday - from the network, not from a bootstrap, and I'm now up to block 220888 without any abnormal memory usage.\n\n```\n  PID USER      PR  NI    VIRT    RES    SHR S  %CPU %MEM     TIME+ COMMAND                                                                                                                    \n 9138 debian    20   0  578000 390180   1704 S   6.0 21.6 131:51.95 bitcoind           \n```\n",
